<p>
  This is my custom romanisation system for Cantonese,
  as spoken and perceived by me.
</p>


<@2> Initials (聲) | initials </@2>


<=>
  <@i>
    (p p' m f) | #labial | Labial
  </@i>
  <@i>
    (t t' n l) | #plain | Plain dental/alveolar
  </@i>
  <@i>
    (k k' ng h kw k'w w) | #velar-glottal | Velar and glottal
  </@i>
  <@i>
    (ts ch ts' ch' s sh y) | #sibilant-palatal | Sibilant dental/alveolar and palatal
  </@i>
</=>

